manual utilisation nano esp32 : 
https://docs.arduino.cc/tutorials/nano-esp32/cheat-sheet/

Reset the Arduino bootloader on the Nano ESP32
https://support.arduino.cc/hc/en-us/articles/9810414060188-Reset-the-Arduino-bootloader-on-the-Nano-ESP32

all the configuration should be set-up only in the fils : 
 -config_robots.c 
 -config_robots.hh

the trigonometrie of the pamis is the same as the big robot. 
0° --> at the direction of the kitchen 
positive rotation --> clockwise direction  ( negative rotaion are accepted)
movement --> all express in milimeter ( negative value are accepted )

/// movement function/// 
straight(mm)
rotate (degrées)
go_to(x_mm,y_mm)